Interface StoreCache

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Consumer<SqlGraphStore>, Supplier<SqlGraphStore>
    public interface StoreCache
extends Supplier<SqlGraphStore>, Consumer<SqlGraphStore>
    Cache for Graph Stores, which supplies an SqlGraphStore object for use, and then accepts it back again for reuse later.

    This ensures that resources are shared or closed as appropriate.
